Angle dependent reflection mapping in spectral range of 400 nm to 800 nm of (a) CZTSe solar cell without ZnO nanorod arrays, and CZTSe solar cells with ZnO nanorod arrays grown for (b) three hours, (c) six hours, (d) nine hours, and (e) twelve hours. (f) The average reflectance of CZTSe solar cells with different ZnO nanorod arrays at different angles. (g) The weighted reflectance of all cells.Figure 4
